1. "*Bako* je učio u školi." (Grandpa went to school.)
2. "*Bakom* se igralo u parku." (Grandpa played in the park.)
3. "*Baku* su često posjećivali." (People often visited Grandpa.)
4. "Njegov *bako* je bio ljubazan prema njemu." (His Grandpa was kind to him.)
5. "On je bio najponosniji na svojeg *baka*." (He was most proud of his Grandpa.)